1
00:01:53,800 --> 00:01:54,800
All right.

2
00:01:56,479 --> 00:01:57,640
Keep it a secret.

3
00:01:58,720 --> 00:02:00,200
Don't let the kid know.

4
00:02:17,720 --> 00:02:18,520
What's wrong?

5
00:02:23,120 --> 00:02:23,920
What's wrong?

6
00:02:24,520 --> 00:02:25,120
Well,

7
00:02:25,200 --> 00:02:28,079
the teacher asked me to buy an English dictation tape,

8
00:02:28,079 --> 00:02:29,210
and I'm out of money.

9
00:02:29,840 --> 00:02:30,900
I'll get it for you.

10
00:02:34,800 --> 00:02:36,760
Mom, what's wrong?

11
00:02:37,000 --> 00:02:37,860
Are you crying?

12
00:02:38,960 --> 00:02:40,920
I just put in some eye drops.

13
00:02:40,960 --> 00:02:42,200
I don't know what's wrong today.

14
00:02:42,200 --> 00:02:43,200
My eyes

15
00:02:43,640 --> 00:02:45,300
keep feeling uncomfortable.

16
00:02:46,600 --> 00:02:47,720
Here, take it all.

17
00:02:48,360 --> 00:02:49,440
This is so much.

18
00:02:49,520 --> 00:02:50,250
Is it enough?

19
00:02:50,440 --> 00:02:51,560
Of course it's enough.

20
00:02:51,560 --> 00:02:52,820
Go to sleep early, son.

21
00:02:53,720 --> 00:02:54,520
Got it, Mom.

22
00:02:55,240 --> 00:02:56,120
Go to sleep.

23
00:02:56,160 --> 00:02:56,890
Thanks, Dad.

24
00:03:09,800 --> 00:03:10,800
The drama performance.

25
00:03:10,800 --> 00:03:12,730
Don't you want to show your talent?

26
00:03:14,640 --> 00:03:15,600
From now until the summer vacation,

27
00:03:15,600 --> 00:03:17,560
there is a city track and field selection competition.

28
00:03:17,560 --> 00:03:19,079
I have to leave to prepare for a while,

29
00:03:19,079 --> 00:03:20,410
so I won't participate.

30
00:03:21,640 --> 00:03:23,880
You are participating for Yuanbao, right?

31
00:03:23,880 --> 00:03:25,340
What role are you playing?

32
00:03:27,280 --> 00:03:29,560
I guess she must be Zixia.

33
00:03:30,079 --> 00:03:31,600
So I have to play Joker.

34
00:03:33,520 --> 00:03:34,720
The secret I told you,

35
00:03:34,880 --> 00:03:35,940
you can't tell her.

36
00:03:36,160 --> 00:03:37,040
Don't worry.

37
00:03:38,400 --> 00:03:39,040
By the way,

38
00:03:39,280 --> 00:03:40,680
about our grandparents,

39
00:03:40,720 --> 00:03:41,680
keep an eye on it.

40
00:03:42,000 --> 00:03:43,360
I think it's very important.

41
00:03:43,360 --> 00:03:44,640
I care more than you do.

42
00:03:45,280 --> 00:03:47,280
But we have to work on Yuanbao first.

43
00:03:47,840 --> 00:03:49,400
Come on, let's compete.

44
00:03:50,600 --> 00:03:52,460
Showing off in front of an expert.

45
00:03:52,680 --> 00:03:54,280
Then, expert, are you ready?

46
00:03:54,600 --> 00:03:56,840
I will count to three. Listen carefully.

47
00:03:56,840 --> 00:03:58,079
Ready... Three!

48
00:03:58,840 --> 00:04:00,040
Why are you cheating?

49
00:04:02,640 --> 00:04:04,840
If heaven gave me another chance,

50
00:04:05,200 --> 00:04:07,200
I would say three words to that girl:

51
00:04:07,520 --> 00:04:08,440
"I love you."

52
00:04:08,760 --> 00:04:10,720
If I had to put a time limit

53
00:04:10,720 --> 00:04:12,240
on this love,

54
00:04:12,560 --> 00:04:15,000
I hope it would be 10,000 years.

55
00:04:24,400 --> 00:04:25,240
No, no.

56
00:04:25,960 --> 00:04:28,240
I'm so nervous even when I'm acting alone.

57
00:04:28,240 --> 00:04:30,400
What will I do when I perform on stage?

58
00:04:30,440 --> 00:04:32,970
What should I do? I won't even be able to speak.

59
00:04:33,840 --> 00:04:34,360
No, no.

60
00:04:34,680 --> 00:04:36,720
Xiong Yuanbao, you have to pull yourself together.

61
00:04:36,720 --> 00:04:39,040
I will get it together.

62
00:04:39,280 --> 00:04:40,640
You can do this, Xiong Yuanbao.

63
00:04:40,640 --> 00:04:41,920
You are the best.

64
00:04:42,080 --> 00:04:44,080
You are the next Oscar Best Actress.

65
00:04:49,320 --> 00:04:50,250
Why are you here?

66
00:04:55,159 --> 00:04:56,090
Have some water.

67
00:04:57,280 --> 00:04:57,960
Thank you.

68
00:05:04,720 --> 00:05:05,650
Feeling better?

69
00:05:08,040 --> 00:05:08,840
Much better.

70
00:05:09,440 --> 00:05:10,080
By the way,

71
00:05:10,800 --> 00:05:13,800
thank you for also recommending 'A Chinese Odyssey'.

72
00:05:14,000 --> 00:05:16,400
We're desk mates. It's the least I could do.

73
00:05:16,840 --> 00:05:17,640
Besides,

74
00:05:18,640 --> 00:05:19,970
I want to ask you a favor,

75
00:05:20,240 --> 00:05:21,640
a presumptuous request.

76
00:05:22,480 --> 00:05:23,320
You saved me.

77
00:05:23,720 --> 00:05:24,960
Tell me, what do you need?

78
00:05:24,960 --> 00:05:26,560
I'll help you as much as I can.

79
00:05:27,600 --> 00:05:28,860
I want to try for Joker.

80
00:05:29,280 --> 00:05:30,960
Would you act with me?

81
00:05:38,240 --> 00:05:39,370
Is it too much to ask?

82
00:05:40,159 --> 00:05:40,840
No.

83
00:05:41,000 --> 00:05:42,800
It's not hard. I can do it.

84
00:05:46,760 --> 00:05:47,600
What's this?

85
00:05:48,000 --> 00:05:50,040
I picked some good clips,

86
00:05:50,440 --> 00:05:51,880
and printed out the corresponding lines.

87
00:05:51,880 --> 00:05:52,680
Take a look.

88
00:05:54,320 --> 00:05:55,920
You are amazing.

89
00:05:58,640 --> 00:05:59,880
But I heard

90
00:06:00,400 --> 00:06:03,640
Yaqi also wants the role of Fairy Zixia.

91
00:06:04,480 --> 00:06:06,080
If you act with her,

92
00:06:06,160 --> 00:06:07,960
your chances of winning will be higher.

93
00:06:07,960 --> 00:06:09,440
Why did you choose me?

94
00:06:10,000 --> 00:06:11,130
I'm looking forward

95
00:06:12,240 --> 00:06:14,300
to Yuanbao's version of Fairy Zixia.

96
00:06:14,360 --> 00:06:16,120
If you don't play Fairy Zixia,

97
00:06:16,560 --> 00:06:18,920
I'm not interested in Joker either.

98
00:06:20,960 --> 00:06:22,020
You must work hard.

99
00:06:22,560 --> 00:06:23,760
I'll be watching you.

100
00:06:26,040 --> 00:06:28,000
Okay, I will.

101
00:06:28,720 --> 00:06:30,120
I know an acting teacher.

102
00:06:30,240 --> 00:06:31,700
Are you free after school?

103
00:06:32,000 --> 00:06:33,360
I'll ask her for some guidance.

104
00:06:33,360 --> 00:06:34,420
Let's go together.

105
00:06:35,200 --> 00:06:35,960
Really?

106
00:06:36,400 --> 00:06:37,960
Can I go with you?

107
00:06:38,080 --> 00:06:38,880
Of course.

108
00:06:41,240 --> 00:06:41,680
Okay.

109
00:06:47,400 --> 00:06:47,930
Yuanbao.

110
00:06:47,960 --> 00:06:49,159
I'm in a rush to my tutoring class.

111
00:06:49,159 --> 00:06:49,840
I'm leaving now.

112
00:06:49,840 --> 00:06:50,760
Okay, go.

113
00:06:50,800 --> 00:06:51,480
Okay, bye.

114
00:06:52,159 --> 00:06:53,280
Are you ready?

115
00:06:54,040 --> 00:06:54,640
Almost.

116
00:06:56,280 --> 00:06:58,680
Do you need to call your family to tell them?

117
00:06:59,159 --> 00:07:01,280
I've already texted my family.

118
00:07:01,320 --> 00:07:03,360
I told them I'm at school

119
00:07:03,840 --> 00:07:06,370
and will go back after finishing my homework.

120
00:07:06,600 --> 00:07:07,200
By the way,

121
00:07:07,400 --> 00:07:08,840
where does the teacher live?

122
00:07:08,840 --> 00:07:10,240
How are we getting there?

123
00:07:10,720 --> 00:07:11,450
It's not far.

124
00:07:11,640 --> 00:07:13,040
Just a ten-minute walk.

125
00:07:14,760 --> 00:07:15,400
Shorty,

126
00:07:15,480 --> 00:07:16,920
I'm taking you somewhere. Hurry up.

127
00:07:16,920 --> 00:07:17,760
Wait.

128
00:07:19,000 --> 00:07:19,640
What's wrong?

129
00:07:19,640 --> 00:07:22,120
I have plans with Meng Jingu today

130
00:07:22,160 --> 00:07:24,760
to study acting at the acting teacher's house.

131
00:07:24,840 --> 00:07:25,970
Go back by yourself.

132
00:07:28,640 --> 00:07:29,570
Acting teacher?

133
00:07:30,320 --> 00:07:31,180
Male or female?

134
00:07:31,360 --> 00:07:33,159
Don't worry, she's a woman.

135
00:07:34,000 --> 00:07:34,680
Yuanbao,

136
00:07:34,920 --> 00:07:36,960
I want to take you to a very important place.

137
00:07:36,960 --> 00:07:39,080
Can't we see this acting teacher later?

138
00:07:39,080 --> 00:07:40,480
She's usually very busy.

139
00:07:40,600 --> 00:07:41,840
Seeing her today

140
00:07:42,159 --> 00:07:43,560
was arranged in advance.

141
00:07:43,640 --> 00:07:45,040
If we go see her tomorrow,

142
00:07:45,080 --> 00:07:47,040
I can't guarantee she'll have time.

143
00:07:47,040 --> 00:07:47,840
And for Yuanbao and me

144
00:07:47,840 --> 00:07:49,840
to learn some professional knowledge,

145
00:07:49,840 --> 00:07:51,300
it's also very necessary.

146
00:07:51,480 --> 00:07:52,920
That's right, exactly.

147
00:07:55,760 --> 00:07:56,690
Then I'll go too.

148
00:07:57,520 --> 00:07:58,780
What are you going for?

149
00:07:59,520 --> 00:08:01,280
I'm a member of the group after all.

150
00:08:01,280 --> 00:08:02,400
Why can't I go?

151
00:08:03,200 --> 00:08:04,080
Besides,

152
00:08:04,400 --> 00:08:06,260
don't I have to pick a role to play?

153
00:08:06,320 --> 00:08:07,560
What role are you picking?

154
00:08:07,560 --> 00:08:08,820
None of your business.

155
00:08:08,880 --> 00:08:10,080
Anyway, if I don't go,

156
00:08:10,080 --> 00:08:11,480
Yuanbao can't go either.

157
00:08:12,640 --> 00:08:13,920
What's wrong with you today?

158
00:08:13,920 --> 00:08:15,450
Why are you acting so weird?

159
00:08:16,240 --> 00:08:17,920
Just go away.

160
00:08:19,360 --> 00:08:20,280
No, why won't you

161
00:08:20,280 --> 00:08:21,360
let me go with you?

162
00:08:21,720 --> 00:08:22,800
It's so dark out,

163
00:08:23,040 --> 00:08:24,720
and he's taking you to a strange place.

164
00:08:24,720 --> 00:08:26,050
You don't even know him.

165
00:08:26,200 --> 00:08:27,760
What if he has bad intentions?

166
00:08:27,760 --> 00:08:29,800
You'll have nowhere to cry when the time comes.

167
00:08:29,800 --> 00:08:31,360
Meng Jingu is my desk mate.

168
00:08:31,440 --> 00:08:33,159
How could he have any bad intentions?

169
00:08:33,159 --> 00:08:35,400
Besides, we're going to the teacher's house,

170
00:08:35,400 --> 00:08:37,159
not a lion's den.

171
00:08:37,320 --> 00:08:38,919
You make it sound so scary.

172
00:08:39,440 --> 00:08:41,919
Okay, I know you're worried about me.

173
00:08:42,280 --> 00:08:44,480
But Meng Jingu and I already made plans.

174
00:08:45,400 --> 00:08:46,560
You know,

175
00:08:46,720 --> 00:08:49,520
I really want to play the role of Fairy Zixia well.

176
00:08:50,080 --> 00:08:50,960
Don't worry.

177
00:08:51,320 --> 00:08:52,800
Let's go.

178
00:09:11,360 --> 00:09:13,490
What should I do? I'm a little nervous.

179
00:09:33,520 --> 00:09:35,320
Make sure to review

180
00:09:35,360 --> 00:09:36,600
the lesson the teacher taught today.

181
00:09:36,600 --> 00:09:37,320
Okay.

182
00:09:59,920 --> 00:10:01,200
We're almost at your house.

183
00:10:01,200 --> 00:10:02,600
Yeah, it's just up ahead.

184
00:10:04,040 --> 00:10:06,440
I heard you and Mu Qingyun are neighbors

185
00:10:06,800 --> 00:10:08,000
and grew up together.

186
00:10:08,360 --> 00:10:09,160
That's right.

187
00:10:09,360 --> 00:10:12,440
Our parents were classmates since they were young.

188
00:10:12,720 --> 00:10:14,850
Later, they worked in the same factory

189
00:10:15,040 --> 00:10:17,560
and lived in the same family dormitory.

190
00:10:18,080 --> 00:10:20,560
We were even born in the same hospital.

191
00:10:20,920 --> 00:10:22,380
Isn't that a coincidence?

192
00:10:22,880 --> 00:10:24,680
Then you must know him very well.

193
00:10:24,680 --> 00:10:25,560
More than that.

194
00:10:25,760 --> 00:10:27,420
I even know when he wet the bed.

195
00:10:29,960 --> 00:10:31,360
I mean,

196
00:10:31,760 --> 00:10:33,560
we grew up together.

197
00:10:35,360 --> 00:10:36,600
Have his grades

198
00:10:37,320 --> 00:10:38,580
always been like this?

199
00:10:39,880 --> 00:10:42,680
His grades were okay in elementary school.

200
00:10:43,080 --> 00:10:45,800
Later, he just let himself go,

201
00:10:46,000 --> 00:10:47,560
and his grades plummeted.

202
00:10:48,760 --> 00:10:49,600
I know

203
00:10:50,080 --> 00:10:52,160
good students like you

204
00:10:52,520 --> 00:10:54,840
don't really like students like Mutou.

205
00:10:55,480 --> 00:10:57,680
But Mutou is actually a really good guy.

206
00:10:57,920 --> 00:10:59,600
Besides his poor grades,

207
00:10:59,760 --> 00:11:01,420
he has a lot of good qualities.

208
00:11:02,120 --> 00:11:03,450
Has he never lied to you?

209
00:11:03,640 --> 00:11:04,760
Lied to me?

210
00:11:05,800 --> 00:11:08,060
If he dared to lie to me, he'd be dead meat.

211
00:11:08,280 --> 00:11:09,680
He swore an oath to me.

212
00:11:10,200 --> 00:11:12,000
What's wrong? Has he lied to you?

213
00:11:13,640 --> 00:11:15,440
Nothing. Just making conversation.

214
00:11:15,440 --> 00:11:16,200
Let's go.

215
00:11:25,680 --> 00:11:27,200
Ms. Li is quite humorous.

216
00:11:27,840 --> 00:11:29,240
She is very professional.

217
00:11:29,240 --> 00:11:30,570
Have you learned it all?

218
00:11:31,040 --> 00:11:32,600
I wrote it all down in my notebook.

219
00:11:32,600 --> 00:11:33,480
Don't worry.

220
00:11:34,080 --> 00:11:36,480
Let's find some time to run lines tomorrow.

221
00:11:39,000 --> 00:11:39,680
Mutou,

222
00:11:40,160 --> 00:11:41,490
what are you doing here?

223
00:11:42,760 --> 00:11:45,820
The weather is nice today. I came out for some fresh air.

224
00:11:51,360 --> 00:11:52,600
Why are you just getting back?

225
00:11:52,600 --> 00:11:54,960
Yuanbao and I rehearsed at the teacher's house for a while,

226
00:11:54,960 --> 00:11:56,160
so we were delayed.

227
00:11:56,360 --> 00:11:57,290
But with me here,

228
00:11:57,320 --> 00:11:59,520
you don't have to worry about her safety.

229
00:11:59,520 --> 00:12:01,640
I'm only worried because you're here.

230
00:12:01,640 --> 00:12:03,170
What are you talking about?

231
00:12:04,080 --> 00:12:04,680
Deskmate.

232
00:12:05,000 --> 00:12:06,880
Thanks for taking me to see the teacher today

233
00:12:06,880 --> 00:12:08,000
and walking me back.

234
00:12:08,000 --> 00:12:08,920
It's getting late.

235
00:12:08,920 --> 00:12:09,960
Go back and get some rest.

236
00:12:09,960 --> 00:12:11,760
Okay, I'll head back now.

237
00:12:13,120 --> 00:12:14,080
Goodbye, Zixia.

238
00:12:14,640 --> 00:12:15,840
Goodnight, Joker.

239
00:12:18,200 --> 00:12:19,000
Bye-bye.

240
00:12:22,280 --> 00:12:24,140
What are you doing? Let's go home.

241
00:12:25,600 --> 00:12:27,330
What did that guy mean just now?

242
00:12:27,600 --> 00:12:29,200
What Zixia and Joker?

243
00:12:29,640 --> 00:12:30,480
Are you two...

244
00:12:31,040 --> 00:12:33,200
I know this decision is a bit sudden.

245
00:12:33,240 --> 00:12:34,720
I haven't had time to tell you.

246
00:12:34,720 --> 00:12:36,380
Meng Jingu and I discussed it,

247
00:12:36,400 --> 00:12:38,000
and we plan to act together

248
00:12:38,040 --> 00:12:40,600
to try for the roles of Zixia and Joker.

249
00:12:41,360 --> 00:12:43,220
Why didn't you tell me in advance?

250
00:12:43,600 --> 00:12:45,280
I know that since we were little,

251
00:12:45,280 --> 00:12:47,360
I've always participated in these activities with you.

252
00:12:47,360 --> 00:12:49,440
But haven't you always disliked them?

253
00:12:49,440 --> 00:12:50,440
I thought

254
00:12:51,000 --> 00:12:52,260
I shouldn't force you.

255
00:12:53,440 --> 00:12:54,600
This is a good thing too.

256
00:12:54,600 --> 00:12:56,880
If you didn't want to be with me, just say so.

257
00:12:56,880 --> 00:12:59,120
When did I ever say I was forcing myself to accompany you?

258
00:12:59,120 --> 00:13:00,400
Why have you changed?

259
00:13:00,760 --> 00:13:02,160
Didn't you use to dislike

260
00:13:02,160 --> 00:13:03,240
participating in these kinds of activities

261
00:13:03,240 --> 00:13:04,770
and think they were stupid?

262
00:13:04,960 --> 00:13:07,800
Besides, Meng Jingu is a top student.

263
00:13:07,880 --> 00:13:09,440
If I can act with him,

264
00:13:09,800 --> 00:13:12,260
won't my chances of playing Zixia be better?

265
00:13:13,520 --> 00:13:14,600
Why do you think

266
00:13:14,680 --> 00:13:16,280
he will definitely be Joker?

267
00:13:17,680 --> 00:13:20,440
Let me tell you, the competition hasn't started yet.

268
00:13:20,440 --> 00:13:22,370
It's still uncertain who will win.

269
00:13:22,400 --> 00:13:24,120
If he doesn't get selected as Joker...

270
00:13:24,120 --> 00:13:25,650
Don't be too disappointed.

271
00:13:26,400 --> 00:13:28,240
What do you mean it's up for grabs?

272
00:13:28,240 --> 00:13:29,970
Mutou, are you participating?

273
00:13:30,560 --> 00:13:31,520
Wait for me.

274
00:13:34,480 --> 00:13:37,160
It's just memorizing lines to compete for Zhi Zun Bao.

275
00:13:37,160 --> 00:13:38,220
Anyone can do that.

276
00:13:38,400 --> 00:13:39,400
I'll show you

277
00:13:39,520 --> 00:13:42,360
who the real Zhi Zun Bao is.

278
00:13:45,040 --> 00:13:46,240
You should do this.

279
00:13:47,240 --> 00:13:48,720
I deserve to die too.

280
00:13:50,000 --> 00:13:51,920
Once, there was a sincere love.

281
00:14:27,080 --> 00:14:28,040
Stop.

282
00:14:53,000 --> 00:14:54,320
Bro, why did you just

283
00:14:54,320 --> 00:14:56,450
shout 'shut up' during the open class?

284
00:15:01,400 --> 00:15:04,530
Don't bring it up. It makes me mad just thinking about it.

285
00:15:10,200 --> 00:15:10,800
You two,

286
00:15:10,840 --> 00:15:13,000
um, I'll be taking my leave now.

287
00:15:18,680 --> 00:15:20,140
Mind having a chat with me?

288
00:15:22,720 --> 00:15:23,850
It's about Yuanbao.

289
00:15:24,520 --> 00:15:26,050
Don't you want to talk to me?

290
00:15:28,560 --> 00:15:29,820
What do you want to say?

291
00:15:31,000 --> 00:15:32,200
It seems only matters regarding Yuanbao

292
00:15:32,200 --> 00:15:33,400
can make you care.

293
00:15:33,840 --> 00:15:35,960
Cut the crap. Just say it.

294
00:15:36,200 --> 00:15:36,680
But right now,

295
00:15:36,680 --> 00:15:39,480
I suddenly don't want to talk about Yuanbao anymore.

296
00:15:39,480 --> 00:15:41,600
Are you tricking me?

297
00:15:42,840 --> 00:15:45,200
Forget it. I'll just be straightforward.

298
00:15:51,960 --> 00:15:53,420
'A Brief History of Time.'

299
00:15:53,720 --> 00:15:55,320
I still recognize these words.

300
00:15:55,320 --> 00:15:56,320
Stop pretending.

301
00:15:57,400 --> 00:15:59,160
You are clearly a physics genius.

302
00:15:59,160 --> 00:16:00,080
Why did you pretend to know nothing

303
00:16:00,080 --> 00:16:01,160
in the class?

304
00:16:01,960 --> 00:16:02,880
You didn't cheat on the physics test.

305
00:16:02,880 --> 00:16:03,960
Why did you admit it

306
00:16:04,040 --> 00:16:05,370
and say you copied mine?

307
00:16:05,680 --> 00:16:06,610
What do you mean?

308
00:16:06,800 --> 00:16:07,860
Why did you do that?

309
00:16:08,760 --> 00:16:09,520
I know.

310
00:16:09,960 --> 00:16:11,600
You are Alpha.

311
00:16:19,160 --> 00:16:21,640
No wonder. He is Gamma.

312
00:16:22,560 --> 00:16:24,600
It's a small world.

313
00:16:25,720 --> 00:16:28,160
Fine. Since you've brought it up,

314
00:16:28,800 --> 00:16:31,000
there's no need for me to hide it anymore.

315
00:16:31,000 --> 00:16:32,440
I can tell you,

316
00:16:33,000 --> 00:16:35,060
but you must swear to keep it a secret.

317
00:16:44,560 --> 00:16:45,360
Actually,

318
00:16:46,160 --> 00:16:47,400
Yuanbao and I

319
00:16:48,200 --> 00:16:49,680
are not from around here.

320
00:16:50,800 --> 00:16:52,080
Not from around here?

321
00:16:57,440 --> 00:16:58,360
Yuanbao and I

322
00:16:59,120 --> 00:17:00,440
are actually from the distant

323
00:17:00,440 --> 00:17:01,800
Blablabla Planet.

324
00:17:02,720 --> 00:17:04,640
Our planet was attacked

325
00:17:04,640 --> 00:17:06,599
by Hulahulahula aliens.

326
00:17:07,160 --> 00:17:08,319
I, as a prince,

327
00:17:08,520 --> 00:17:09,780
and she, as a princess,

328
00:17:10,079 --> 00:17:11,960
arrived on Earth

329
00:17:12,160 --> 00:17:14,690
under the desperate escort of our ministers.

330
00:17:14,800 --> 00:17:16,460
The ministers who escorted us

331
00:17:17,160 --> 00:17:18,819
also sacrificed themselves.

332
00:17:19,440 --> 00:17:22,200
We are the only survivors

333
00:17:22,240 --> 00:17:23,599
of Blablabla Planet.

334
00:17:24,319 --> 00:17:26,849
So we have to desperately hide our identities

335
00:17:27,319 --> 00:17:28,480
to survive.

336
00:17:29,800 --> 00:17:31,400
Do people from Blabla Planet

337
00:17:31,440 --> 00:17:32,770
also like to drink coke?

338
00:17:35,160 --> 00:17:36,160
We have no choice.

339
00:17:37,120 --> 00:17:38,240
We have to survive.

340
00:17:38,760 --> 00:17:39,480
Also,

341
00:17:39,600 --> 00:17:41,200
we are not from Blabla Planet,

342
00:17:41,200 --> 00:17:42,720
but Blablabla.

343
00:17:43,080 --> 00:17:44,410
I haven't finished yet.

344
00:17:44,800 --> 00:17:46,800
Our planet has explicit rules

345
00:17:46,920 --> 00:17:48,880
that we can't get too close to Earthlings.

346
00:17:48,880 --> 00:17:50,400
Yuanbao has a special constitution.

347
00:17:50,400 --> 00:17:51,800
If she interacts with you Earthlings,

348
00:17:51,800 --> 00:17:53,280
especially men like you,

349
00:17:53,400 --> 00:17:55,080
and has too much physical contact,

350
00:17:55,080 --> 00:17:56,810
it will shorten your lifespan.

351
00:17:56,840 --> 00:17:57,680
I'm not trying to scare you.

352
00:17:57,680 --> 00:17:58,760
Do you understand?

353
00:18:01,200 --> 00:18:03,660
Aren't you being punished to stand? Go back.

354
00:18:04,800 --> 00:18:06,200
I'm telling you a secret.

355
00:18:06,240 --> 00:18:08,400
I'm only saying this because I see you as a bro.

356
00:18:08,400 --> 00:18:09,760
You beat around the bush

357
00:18:10,520 --> 00:18:13,180
just to stop me from acting with Yuanbao, right?

358
00:18:13,480 --> 00:18:14,280
No.

359
00:18:15,400 --> 00:18:16,840
Of course, if you don't want

360
00:18:16,840 --> 00:18:18,360
your internal organs to be jinxed by her

361
00:18:18,360 --> 00:18:19,360
and burst!

362
00:18:20,000 --> 00:18:20,480
That would be so tragic.

363
00:18:20,480 --> 00:18:22,140
You'd better drop it, really.

364
00:18:23,840 --> 00:18:25,040
I'm the kind of person

365
00:18:25,440 --> 00:18:27,370
who has a really strong curiosity.

366
00:18:27,720 --> 00:18:28,680
I'm also

367
00:18:28,840 --> 00:18:29,900
very competitive.

368
00:18:30,400 --> 00:18:31,800
Since you put it that way,

369
00:18:31,960 --> 00:18:34,000
I simply must act with Yuanbao.

370
00:18:34,240 --> 00:18:35,280
I'll see if

371
00:18:35,360 --> 00:18:37,840
my internal organs will go pfft-pfft.

372
00:18:42,840 --> 00:18:44,080
Then you're dead.

373
00:18:45,280 --> 00:18:48,520
Your internal organs will go pfft-pfft sooner or later.

374
00:18:51,360 --> 00:18:54,200
Someone told a huge lie

375
00:18:54,280 --> 00:18:55,480
and fooled everyone,

376
00:18:55,920 --> 00:18:57,050
including Yuanbao.

377
00:18:59,040 --> 00:19:00,440
When your lie is exposed,

378
00:19:01,040 --> 00:19:02,400
will your internal organs

379
00:19:02,400 --> 00:19:04,000
be the ones going pfft-pfft?

380
00:19:08,720 --> 00:19:11,000
Alpha, don't forget,

381
00:19:11,600 --> 00:19:13,130
you still owe me a question.

382
00:19:13,880 --> 00:19:14,920
So from now on,

383
00:19:15,040 --> 00:19:16,900
including the role of Zhi Zun Bao,

384
00:19:16,960 --> 00:19:18,240
I won't lose to you.

385
00:19:25,200 --> 00:19:26,680
I didn't expect

386
00:19:27,200 --> 00:19:28,760
that he is Gamma.

387
00:19:29,040 --> 00:19:31,960
Was this guy a fighting cock in his past life?

388
00:19:34,960 --> 00:19:35,720
He

389
00:19:36,040 --> 00:19:38,160
won't tell Yuanbao my secret, right?

390
00:19:46,520 --> 00:19:47,280
Ning Yu,

391
00:19:47,760 --> 00:19:48,840
leave it to me.

392
00:19:54,160 --> 00:19:54,690
Oh my god.

393
00:19:54,720 --> 00:19:55,640
Class Monitor.

394
00:19:56,160 --> 00:19:57,020
Class Monitor.

395
00:19:57,960 --> 00:19:58,960
I'm sorry, Class Monitor.

396
00:19:58,960 --> 00:19:59,640
Are you okay?

397
00:19:59,640 --> 00:20:00,360
I didn't mean it.

398
00:20:00,360 --> 00:20:01,120
Are you okay?

399
00:20:01,400 --> 00:20:02,200
I'm fine.

400
00:20:03,720 --> 00:20:05,720
It's all red, how can you be fine?

401
00:20:06,000 --> 00:20:07,240
Well, I'll take you to the infirmary.

402
00:20:07,240 --> 00:20:08,500
You guys keep playing.

403
00:20:08,720 --> 00:20:09,850
Let's go take a look.

404
00:20:09,920 --> 00:20:10,560
Let's go.

405
00:20:13,960 --> 00:20:15,040
I'm sorry.

406
00:20:18,840 --> 00:20:19,560
Qingyun,

407
00:20:19,840 --> 00:20:22,200
thank you for taking me to the Western Pharmacy.

408
00:20:22,200 --> 00:20:23,760
I'm actually fine.

409
00:20:24,640 --> 00:20:25,800
I'm really sorry.

410
00:20:26,200 --> 00:20:27,600
We didn't mean to

411
00:20:28,520 --> 00:20:29,850
hit your head like that.

412
00:20:30,120 --> 00:20:32,520
If it still hurts, remember to come find us.

413
00:20:36,160 --> 00:20:37,960
Yuanbao is so serious recently.

414
00:20:38,120 --> 00:20:41,000
I heard she's going to act with Meng Jingu.

415
00:20:42,520 --> 00:20:46,600
If I also want to fight for the role of Zixia Fairy,

416
00:20:47,200 --> 00:20:49,160
are you willing to act with me?

417
00:20:52,600 --> 00:20:53,400
It's okay.

418
00:20:53,600 --> 00:20:54,280
I know

419
00:20:54,480 --> 00:20:56,520
you have such a good relationship with Yuanbao.

420
00:20:56,520 --> 00:20:57,520
I can understand.

421
00:21:04,400 --> 00:21:05,120
Alright.

422
00:21:09,680 --> 00:21:10,600
I promise you.

423
00:21:11,240 --> 00:21:13,400
You play Zixia, and I'll play Zhizunbao.

424
00:21:13,400 --> 00:21:14,640
Is that really okay?

425
00:21:19,080 --> 00:21:20,280
Why not?

426
00:21:20,560 --> 00:21:21,620
As long as I'm here,

427
00:21:21,720 --> 00:21:23,580
we will definitely win the roles.

428
00:21:34,360 --> 00:21:35,600
What about Yuanbao?

429
00:21:48,680 --> 00:21:49,400
Yuanbao,

430
00:21:50,680 --> 00:21:51,440
are you okay?

431
00:21:52,840 --> 00:21:53,480
I'm fine.

432
00:21:54,040 --> 00:21:55,240
Let's run the lines.

433
00:21:56,520 --> 00:21:57,850
We will definitely win.

434
00:22:01,360 --> 00:22:02,000
Come on.

435
00:22:06,840 --> 00:22:07,840
Why do you want to act

436
00:22:07,840 --> 00:22:09,680
with the class monitor today?

437
00:22:11,920 --> 00:22:13,480
What? You wanna control me?

438
00:22:13,800 --> 00:22:14,920
No, I don't.

439
00:22:15,840 --> 00:22:17,320
But then again,

440
00:22:17,600 --> 00:22:18,840
did you force yourself to choose Joker

441
00:22:18,840 --> 00:22:20,500
just because you wanted to act

442
00:22:20,640 --> 00:22:22,520
with the class monitor?

443
00:22:23,200 --> 00:22:24,660
I'm kindly reminding you.

444
00:22:24,920 --> 00:22:26,850
If you really want to participate,

445
00:22:26,920 --> 00:22:28,920
I advise you to choose another role.

446
00:22:29,200 --> 00:22:31,730
I'm afraid you can't compete with Meng Jingu.

447
00:22:32,720 --> 00:22:34,600
I just don't understand

448
00:22:34,840 --> 00:22:36,800
what's so good about Meng Jingu

449
00:22:36,960 --> 00:22:38,600
that makes you place such high hopes on him.

450
00:22:38,600 --> 00:22:39,720
You don't even know

451
00:22:39,800 --> 00:22:41,530
what this guy has up his sleeve.

452
00:22:41,680 --> 00:22:43,160
He might ditch you halfway

453
00:22:43,240 --> 00:22:44,770
to act with someone better.

454
00:22:47,360 --> 00:22:48,760
What are you laughing at?

455
00:22:48,920 --> 00:22:50,800
Meng Jingu is excellent in character and learning.

456
00:22:50,800 --> 00:22:51,730
He's a gentleman

457
00:22:52,080 --> 00:22:54,120
who always keeps his promises.

458
00:22:54,320 --> 00:22:56,120
I'm just trying to make progress

459
00:22:56,360 --> 00:22:58,360
by acting with the top student in our grade.

460
00:22:58,360 --> 00:22:59,360
This way,

461
00:22:59,480 --> 00:23:01,600
my grades will improve faster.

462
00:23:01,920 --> 00:23:02,600
Fine.

463
00:23:02,800 --> 00:23:04,440
The midterms are coming up.

464
00:23:05,000 --> 00:23:07,360
I'd like to see if your grades can improve.

465
00:23:08,480 --> 00:23:11,040
With his all-around development,

466
00:23:11,240 --> 00:23:13,480
it'll be convenient to ask him questions I don't know.

467
00:23:13,480 --> 00:23:14,280
Besides,

468
00:23:14,480 --> 00:23:17,140
I've always been working harder than you, okay?

469
00:23:23,960 --> 00:23:25,160
Let's read it when we get home.

470
00:23:25,160 --> 00:23:25,880
I'm hungry.

471
00:23:34,280 --> 00:23:35,960
Better to rely on yourself.

472
00:23:36,000 --> 00:23:36,730
Some say that

473
00:23:36,760 --> 00:23:37,960
every high school student

474
00:23:37,960 --> 00:23:39,640
is like a lonely warrior,

475
00:23:40,000 --> 00:23:41,330
fighting alone in every

476
00:23:41,360 --> 00:23:43,000
cold late night.

477
00:23:43,440 --> 00:23:44,800
Those sets of test papers

478
00:23:44,800 --> 00:23:46,400
and workbooks

479
00:23:46,480 --> 00:23:48,760
are the stepping stones to our dreams.

480
00:23:49,000 --> 00:23:51,480
We just have to keep working hard.

481
00:23:51,640 --> 00:23:53,920
Only then can we stand higher and see further,

482
00:23:53,920 --> 00:23:56,520
and witness scenery we have never seen before.

483
00:23:56,600 --> 00:23:57,440
Zixia,

484
00:23:57,520 --> 00:23:58,680
I will work hard too.

485
00:24:27,120 --> 00:24:27,360
Chemistry...

486
00:24:27,360 --> 00:24:27,600
Chem... Mr. Xu.

487
00:24:27,600 --> 00:24:28,600
Um, Mr. Xu.

488
00:24:29,080 --> 00:24:29,920
Outside of work,

489
00:24:29,920 --> 00:24:31,200
what are your hobbies?

490
00:24:31,520 --> 00:24:32,800
I like working out,

491
00:24:32,840 --> 00:24:33,400
and

492
00:24:33,440 --> 00:24:35,570
occasionally enjoy watching movies.

493
00:24:41,200 --> 00:24:43,000
"Call for Love".

494
00:24:44,280 --> 00:24:46,010
"Love Cannot be Transferred".

495
00:24:47,560 --> 00:24:49,000
"Secret".

496
00:24:49,680 --> 00:24:50,610
This one is good.

497
00:24:55,560 --> 00:24:56,160
Hello.

498
00:24:56,320 --> 00:24:58,120
I want two tickets for 'Secret'.

499
00:25:50,640 --> 00:25:52,000
Grandma, I'm back.

500
00:25:52,840 --> 00:25:54,040
Yuanbao is back.

501
00:25:56,040 --> 00:25:57,440
Wash your hands quickly.

502
00:25:57,560 --> 00:26:00,290
We're going to Qingyun's house for dinner later.

503
00:26:01,200 --> 00:26:02,600
How did you do on the exam?

504
00:26:04,040 --> 00:26:05,080
Not bad.

505
00:26:06,240 --> 00:26:09,080
You have to study hard.

506
00:26:09,600 --> 00:26:10,240
All right.

507
00:26:10,240 --> 00:26:11,440
I got it.

508
00:26:14,400 --> 00:26:15,480
My stomach hurts.

509
00:26:15,720 --> 00:26:16,880
I'm going to the bathroom.

510
00:26:16,880 --> 00:26:18,000
Wait, did you

511
00:26:18,240 --> 00:26:19,120
eat something bad

512
00:26:19,120 --> 00:26:20,720
outside again?

513
00:26:24,760 --> 00:26:25,890
By the way, Grandma.

514
00:26:25,920 --> 00:26:28,520
We're having a parent-teacher meeting tomorrow.

515
00:26:28,520 --> 00:26:29,160
I know.

516
00:26:29,320 --> 00:26:30,720
Your aunt will go for you,

517
00:26:30,800 --> 00:26:32,520
and Mr. Mu will go for Qingyun.

518
00:26:32,880 --> 00:26:34,680
Hasn't it always been like this?

519
00:26:35,360 --> 00:26:36,080
I got it.

520
00:26:43,280 --> 00:26:44,240
This child.

521
00:26:45,640 --> 00:26:47,920
She must really want her parents

522
00:26:48,160 --> 00:26:50,360
to attend her parent-teacher meeting.

523
00:26:51,960 --> 00:26:53,640
Son, this time,

524
00:26:53,720 --> 00:26:55,080
you did well on your exam.

525
00:26:55,080 --> 00:26:56,200
Your teacher, Mr. Tian,

526
00:26:56,200 --> 00:26:57,600
is full of praise for you.

527
00:26:57,800 --> 00:26:58,930
Mom is very pleased.

528
00:27:00,720 --> 00:27:01,560
Brat.

529
00:27:02,040 --> 00:27:03,760
Here, take this.

530
00:27:04,560 --> 00:27:05,760
This is your reward.

531
00:27:06,160 --> 00:27:07,160
You did a good job.

532
00:27:07,960 --> 00:27:09,520
Don't you like sneakers?

533
00:27:09,800 --> 00:27:11,060
Go buy them if you like.

534
00:27:11,200 --> 00:27:12,760
As long as you get good grades,

535
00:27:12,760 --> 00:27:14,290
Dad will give you anything.

536
00:27:16,080 --> 00:27:17,760
Son, take it.

537
00:27:18,560 --> 00:27:20,620
You did an excellent job on this exam.

538
00:27:20,920 --> 00:27:22,280
Your dad is very happy.

539
00:27:22,760 --> 00:27:24,490
Keep up the good work next time.

540
00:27:24,760 --> 00:27:25,680
I don't need it.

541
00:27:26,560 --> 00:27:28,290
Isn't first place all you want?

542
00:27:28,560 --> 00:27:30,560
Isn't it enough that I gave it to you?

543
00:27:30,600 --> 00:27:31,760
What are you saying?

544
00:27:33,520 --> 00:27:35,320
You don't want the money, right?

545
00:27:37,320 --> 00:27:38,780
Is having money a big deal?

546
00:27:42,200 --> 00:27:43,160
This brat,

547
00:27:43,600 --> 00:27:45,060
how dare he talk back to me.

548
00:27:45,160 --> 00:27:45,960
All right.

549
00:27:46,040 --> 00:27:47,320
You have a bad heart.

550
00:27:57,200 --> 00:27:58,080
Ruirui, this...

551
00:27:58,080 --> 00:27:58,800
Shang Ningyu,

552
00:27:58,800 --> 00:27:59,720
what a coincidence.

553
00:27:59,720 --> 00:28:00,800
What are you doing so late?

554
00:28:00,800 --> 00:28:02,060
I just finished class.

555
00:28:02,280 --> 00:28:03,840
You're out so late...

556
00:28:03,960 --> 00:28:06,000
I... I'm exercising.

557
00:28:06,440 --> 00:28:07,970
You brat! Stop right there!

558
00:28:08,560 --> 00:28:09,600
Ruirui, I have to go.

559
00:28:09,600 --> 00:28:10,280
Gotta run for my life!

560
00:28:10,280 --> 00:28:12,600
You got a low score again and made me sit in the special seat!

561
00:28:12,600 --> 00:28:14,160
Let's talk this out.

562
00:28:14,400 --> 00:28:15,280
Shang Ningyu.

563
00:28:18,160 --> 00:28:19,120
Ouch! Mom!

564
00:28:19,160 --> 00:28:21,880
So his mom is this tough.

565
00:28:22,640 --> 00:28:24,040
I'm sorry.

566
00:28:51,320 --> 00:28:52,240
Slippers.

567
00:28:59,360 --> 00:29:00,280
Leave me alone.

568
00:29:03,880 --> 00:29:05,340
I'll go get you some water.

569
00:29:07,880 --> 00:29:08,720
Qiao Yan.

570
00:29:10,960 --> 00:29:12,960
Are your exam results out?

571
00:29:13,600 --> 00:29:14,720
Show them to me.

572
00:29:36,200 --> 00:29:37,160
Hurry up.

573
00:29:43,960 --> 00:29:45,000
What happened?

574
00:29:46,440 --> 00:29:47,900
Your grades are dropping.

575
00:29:48,680 --> 00:29:49,680
Say something!

576
00:29:50,080 --> 00:29:51,000
Are you mute?

577
00:29:52,640 --> 00:29:54,760
I'll be careful next time.

578
00:29:59,320 --> 00:30:00,000
You...

579
00:30:00,280 --> 00:30:02,610
You're getting more and more ridiculous.

580
00:30:06,080 --> 00:30:07,040
Speak!

581
00:30:08,240 --> 00:30:09,080
Are you mute?

582
00:30:31,320 --> 00:30:32,520
Ms. Xu, well...

583
00:30:32,560 --> 00:30:33,680
This weekend, I...

584
00:30:34,680 --> 00:30:36,410
I want to invite you to watch...

585
00:30:37,200 --> 00:30:38,200
Well, we...

586
00:30:42,720 --> 00:30:44,980
Dropping the ball at the crucial moment.

587
00:30:59,040 --> 00:31:01,720
See you at the cinema this weekend.

588
00:31:02,360 --> 00:31:03,560
Be there or be square.

589
00:31:03,840 --> 00:31:06,520
Someone who has admired you for a long time.

590
00:31:10,120 --> 00:31:11,840
Subtle but elegant.

591
00:31:12,480 --> 00:31:14,410
And has a certain sense of mystery.

592
00:31:15,360 --> 00:31:16,360
Awesome!

593
00:31:31,400 --> 00:31:33,200
Well, Ms. Xu.

594
00:31:33,840 --> 00:31:35,040
See you this weekend.

595
00:31:36,480 --> 00:31:38,440
My heart is beating so fast.

596
00:31:40,000 --> 00:31:42,240
My Mr. Right is nearby.

597
00:31:46,040 --> 00:31:48,000
Qingyun, it's your turn.

598
00:31:50,480 --> 00:31:51,480
To where?

599
00:31:52,480 --> 00:31:53,600
Are you tired?

600
00:31:53,840 --> 00:31:55,480
Shall we take a break?

601
00:31:56,400 --> 00:31:57,200
No.

602
00:31:57,960 --> 00:32:00,000
Hearing you say your lines

603
00:32:00,320 --> 00:32:01,650
made me more confident.

604
00:32:01,720 --> 00:32:04,050
We will definitely win the championship.

605
00:32:06,080 --> 00:32:07,410
I've watched this movie

606
00:32:07,560 --> 00:32:09,480
almost eighty-one times.

607
00:32:11,360 --> 00:32:14,090
By the way, Yuanbao has been working hard lately.

608
00:32:14,200 --> 00:32:16,200
I saw her go to the roof just now.

609
00:32:16,480 --> 00:32:18,610
She seemed to be practicing lines too.

610
00:32:20,840 --> 00:32:21,600
The roof?

611
00:32:25,480 --> 00:32:27,880
Well, I'll go check on the enemy.
